            . I am a <rs id="t18151206-151-viclabel822" type="occupation">physician</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18151206-151-victim1264 t18151206-151-viclabel822"></join>, and live at No. 2. <placeName id="t18151206-151-crimeloc823">Bell's-buildings, Salisbury-squate, Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18151206-151-crimeloc823" type="placeName" value="Bell's-buildings, Salisbury-squate, Fleet-street"></interp>
